E109.title: Our history
E109.description: In this world, the Decembrists won, and now Russia has democracy. But there are plenty of problems, too. There are even problems with Romea. It's all because of the schism in Orthodoxy.

E108.title: We rose up and came to an agreement

E107.title: The question of our vassals
E107.description: Vassals, it's time to resolve the issues with them. We'll annex them once we've sorted out everything there.

E231.title: The Emperor's First Plans.
E231.description: The Emperor became the ruler of our German Empire, and we heard from his plans: Seize Alsace, Improve the Economy, Defeat Russia. Simple, but difficult.

E106.title: The end of the Hungarian Republic!
E106.description: Monarchist groups took Budapest and soon subjugated the entire country.

E279.title: Our victory
E279.description: We have won the first elections for communism. We owe it to all our people to carry the revolution throughout our country and then throughout the world!

E222.title: Loss in the 2nd BV.
E222.description: We lost this war. Now we have to pay our allies and still recover from this war.

E229.title: Otto's victory in the elections
E229.description: The great politician and military leader, Otto von Bismarck, won the elections. He declared his readiness to develop the country and make our army great.

E227.title: Choosing a path
E227.description: We've almost completely united Germany, and we need to choose the path we want to take and develop. More precisely, we need to hold elections. The results will determine our path. But who will win?

E104.title: It's time for us to go
E104.description: It's time for us to start a war against Hungary over Transylvania.

E102.title: Transylvania
E102.description: There are huge problems in Transylvania because the Romanians want to collect it and the population there does not want to accept our communism.

E215.title: Wten for Peace
E215.description: Wtenberg agreed to peace. Now they will be peacefully part of us. Hurray.

E103.title: Relations with Romania
E103.description: Things are bad with Romania, they hate us because we have "their" Transylvania.

E101.title: Our communism
E101.description: We are the first communists in Europe and we need to spread the revolution throughout the world.

E226.title: We rose up and came to an agreement

E381.title: The Capitulation of Britain
E381.description: After the defeat of Russia and France, Britain decided to surrender...

E220.title: Let's help Prussia
E220.description: We are allies and we need to help Prussia in such a big war so that it wins.

E328.answer1: This is the end of this path. FOR SATAN!
E328.title: Satan
E328.description: We will show everyone what we are capable of. We will destroy them and build a new world on the ashes. For Us! For Satan!
E328.description1: Thanks for playing and good luck winning. And I also appreciate everything you need to know along the way!

E100.title: Ireland is integrated
E100.description: After a long time, we integrated Ireland and now we have finally united Britain. Hooray.

E366.title: The collapse of France!
E366.description: After a crushing defeat, the French government was able to hold on to its remaining territories and fell into ruin.

E221.title: Loss in 1st BV.
E221.description: We lost this war. Now we have to pay our allies and still recover from this war.

E168.title: Full integration of the South
E168.description: We have fully integrated the south. Now we will have all their industry and are preparing to develop the economy.

E219.title: Peace treaty
E219.description: We took Prague and Nuremberg (Bavaria). After that, Austria began to fall apart and simply couldn't resist, so this is the final victory over Austria and the UNIFICATION OF ALL OF GERMANY.

E358.title: We will help Russia!
E358.description: Russia was attacked by Rome and its ally Germany, we will not allow these two giants to expand even further!

E218.title: 3rd BV.
E218.description: "War on them!" our Kaiser shouted. And we declared war on Austria. Austria is very weak and its people don't want it. The Austrian Empire is almost falling apart. So we won't be able to take Vienna.

E097.title: We are improving the army.
E097.description: We have completed the training and now we are receiving bonuses

E167.title: Military reform
E167.description: The time has come for reform. The first of these will be the Army. Our plan calls for improving our infantry and tanks.

E166.title: First plans
E166.description: The winning party's first plan is to integrate the south. Completely. They don't like the agreement we signed with the southerners.

E349.title: Polish Uprising
E349.description: Polish revolutionaries today proclaimed a new Poland. Now they are ready to seize power by any means necessary!

E096.title: Improving the army
E096.description: It's time for us to improve the army and we'll start with....

E165.title: Victory of the Radicals
E165.description: The radicals won in May and immediately declared that they wanted to create their own Roman Empire. And the Romans were liars and "bad" people.

E214.title: Plan "South"
E214.description: We've already sent them an ultimatum, and several countries have refused to accept it, meaning it will be another war. But a victorious one.

E212.title: Clash with Belgium
E212.description: This morning, our troops were attacked by Belgian troops. This SPG could give us the opportunity to capture and plunder Belgium without any hassle. Do you agree?

E092.title: Wales is integrated!
E092.description: Wales is integrated. As expected, this region will integrate easily. So now Wales is entirely within our borders.

E164.title: Italy
E164.description: We are the new and real Italy

E094.title: Scotland is ours too!
E094.description: We've finally managed to integrate Scotland. But we'll have to fine-tune the integration of Ireland, because Germany is strong, and so is Rome. So the second NCP will have to prepare our TERRIBLE army.

E286.title: Integration of autonomy
E286.description: It's time for us to end autonomy in Austria. This will be a major step toward spreading the revolution even further! After that, we'll also be completely done with the internal affairs, well, almost.

E071.title: Russia invades Poland
E071.description: The Russians invade Poland to suppress the rebels. The entire world provided formal assistance.

E162.title: Joint exercises
E162.description: We conducted joint exercises with Romea. This is another friendly step between the countries.

E161.title: Trade with Romea
E161.description: We were able to reach an agreement with Romea, and we will ultimately benefit. And most importantly, this is an alliance.

E093.title: Beginning of integration
E093.description: Let's now begin integrating Scotland. It will be a bit more difficult this time, though.

E070.title: Polish insurgents
E070.description: They turned to us for help. Will we help them?

E210.title: Army Reform
E210.description: Although we are a great army, any army requires improvements and reforms. The last army reform in our country was in 1821. We need to reform the army in order to defeat our main enemy - Austria.

E160.title: Conservative Victory
E160.description: The Conservatives won the May elections. They immediately stated that they would try to establish ties with Rome, but not with Germany.

E090.title: Problems with Scandinavia
E090.description: We have a bad relationship with Scandinavia. They're a nuisance almost everywhere. Even in the colonies, they're ready to interfere!

E159.title: Elections in our country
E159.description: Today, Italy held its first elections since unification. The winner is...

E209.title: Victory in the second BV.
E209.description: We have defeated and humiliated Austria again. The treaty has already been signed, according to which the entire north is given to us, and we will also try to form an alliance with Holland!

E208.title: Second BV.
E208.description: It's time for us to increase our influence even further. To do this, we need to reduce Austria's influence. By military means.

E207.title: Preparing for the second BV.
E207.description: After the almost complete integration of our alliance, we need to prepare and strike Austria again and strengthen our influence.

E068.title: Congress in the Union
E068.description: Recently, a congress took place in Constantinople. Rome outlined many goals, including war with Russia and attempts to destroy the British colonies.

E206.title: Third integration
E206.description: It's time for us to complete the final integration of our allies. The remaining members of our alliance are very important, so this is a HUGE acquisition.

E155.title: The English
E155.description: They fought us, but now they want to guarantee us. We're becoming necessary. That means we need REFORMS.

E342.title: Ignite a revolution!
E342.description: We will need to help our comrades from Bkrselona, so after their uprising we will help them!

E276.title: The Central Bank of Berlin
E276.description: Recently, as our empire's economy expanded, a central bank was built in Berlin in this honor. Now we are truly on par with Rome.

E352.title: Great victory
E352.description: We've done everything we wanted. Now we're ready to calm down and accept this world. And you, player, thanks for playing. Well, this was supposed to be deluxe, but no!

E089.title: Integration English block
E089.description: The MC integrated the English bloc. We fully agreed on some autonomy within our state. Hurray!

E205.title: The Princess's Legacy
E205.description: From the wedding of our monarch with the Princess of Hanover, our diplomats were able to agree on the complete unification of our countries.

E204.title: Princess?
E204.description: Rumors recently surfaced that the Prussian monarch and the Princess of Hanover were planning to marry. And it was true; they're already married, most likely for love. She's only 18 and he's 30, but it looks like true love.

E154.title: Relationships in the world
E154.description: Although we are the scum of modern Europe, against the backdrop of the growing strength of Prussia and Rome, even we look good to them.

E199.title: Merger with the Alliance
E199.description: We have begun the honest integration of alliance members into our ranks. The first of these will be the small states in the north.

E088.title: Beginning of integration
E088.description: We need to start integrating the English lock in order to strengthen our state and show Europe what we are ready for!

E087.title: Colonies in America
E087.description: The Scandinavians invaded our colony, but due to the weak garrison and the lack of an army nearby...

E288.title: Connections in Hungary
E288.description: We have comrades in Hungary with whom we can achieve a lot. We have already agreed to an alliance between us and to help each other.

E152.title: Colonial development
E152.description: It's time for us to develop our colonies, and the first among them will be Algeria.

E201.title: Fratricidal war
E201.description: We will begin the first skirmish with Austria in order to increase control over Germany.

E200.title: Austria
E200.description: We have bad relations with Austria, it does not want our unification, so we will have to finish with it, and in the meantime, prepare for the first skirmish.

E069.title: Uprising in Poland
E069.description: Today, Polish students took to the streets of Warsaw and rebelled against Russia. They immediately appealed to the German Empire for assistance.

E198.title: Congress of the SGG #1
E198.description: Today, there was a congress of the Council of State's members, where even Austria attended. We discussed many topics, including German reunification. Our alliance was in favor, while the Austrian alliance was against. But we were the majority, so we were allowed to integrate the north.

E191.title: Peaceful annexation
E191.description: After the fall of Austria, the Croatian region begged us. We will take them into our fold.

E086.title: Our economy is weak
E086.description: Our economy is weak compared to Europe's. We need to choose an economic model that will help us catch up and surpass Europe.

E196.title: Our Story #2
E196.description: We are a militant and strong country. Although we still haven't been able to unite Germany, the northern part is already under our considerable influence. And this is the beginning of the new VERSION 2.7.3.

E084.title: Our victory for the Crown
E084.description: We won by taking two important cities. Now we have completely subjugated Iran.

E192.title: The rebels surrendered
E192.description: The rebels in our former puppet states have accepted defeat. Now they're back with us. Hooray!

E085.title: Our history
E085.description: Britain... was the place where an empire should have been, but one uprising shattered it. After the uprising came the Cromwelliansthose who advocate such abominations. Our goal is to become an EMPIRE.

E341.title: Support in Barcelona
E341.description: We need to support the revolutionaries in Brselona; they are also our allies and comrades. Send them aid!

E083.title: Romeya is helping us!
E083.description: Romea decided to help us in our attempts to seize power in Persia.

E082.title: War in Persia
E082.description: A rebellion has broken out in Persia, escalating into civil unrest. Now the entire world is watching with interest.

E307.title: Paktik
E307.description: The peace we need will be here and now.

E252.title: To Paris?
E252.description: Finally, Bismarck decided to go to Paris, France, with whom we have one of the worst relations. But he still managed to reach an agreement. According to the treaty, both we and they would reduce our armies to 25,000 infantrymen. A non-aggression pact was also signed, but most importantly,

E188.title: The Second Monarchy
E188.description: We have a monarchist group rising up in our country.

E151.title: Elections
E151.description: The elections in our country have arrived and the winner is... (France is not finished and will be reworked in 2.8)

E250.title: To Petrograd?
E250.description: Bismarck, as is well known, was one of the best diplomats, and his first goal to prove this was a trip to Petrograd. The meeting lasted about five hours. As a result, a non-aggression pact was signed between Germany and Russia, as well as relations with Russia.

E296.title: The first stage of Hungary's integration
E296.description: We will begin to integrate Hungary so that we can protect its people and strengthen our great union!

E150.title: Our history
E150.description: We lost the war... A BIG AND HUGE STINK, now we are a weak state, it's time to recover

E343.title: Revolution in Barcelona
E343.description: Communists have risen in Barcelona. Although we captured them, they were operating underground and are now ready for war!

E355.title: Division of the Empire
E355.description: We need to make a decision about Austria, whether to make it a puppet or not.

E184.title: We need to go to Africa
E184.description: It's time for us to start colonizing Africa and profit from it.

E149.title: They are with us
E149.description: We put pressure on them, and now they've agreed to join us completely. Even earlier than they expected. Hurray!

E339.title: Bad phrase
E339.description: The Spanish are completely pissed off at the NCS. We must stage a revolution there, say, in Faragon, and then help them. Then we will destroy this Spain!

E148.title: Let's continue
E148.description: We continue to put pressure on Portugal and have already negotiated discounts for ourselves. According to forecasts, we will receive them in full by the beginning of 1854.

E248.title: Campaign in Alsace
E248.description: Today we will cross the border and destroy this "stub." After which we will be able to fully consider ourselves an Empire. And most importantly, Germany will be UNITED AND INDIVIDUAL!

E335.title: Our Switzerland!
E335.description: Today we will start a revolution in Switzerland and liberate its people. Hurrah! For Comrade Marx!

E077.title: Our relationship
E077.description: We have bad relations with the Italians

E247.title: Plan Strasbourg
E247.description: Bismarck, as he had planned, plans to seize Alsace militarily. This will demonstrate our power to France and strengthen our influence over France itself. The plan itself will be put into effect in February of the following year.

E246.title: 'Speech'
E246.description: Otto ascended the platform and began his speech: "We are now a true and great Germany, but we have not proven this to the 'Europeans' because we will show them our power, even if our victory over Austria was not enough for them!" The people rejoiced. Germany will become GREAT.

E180.title: Colonization
E180.description: It's time for us to start colonizing Africa. As a result of co-optation, we will have plenty of resources.

E147.title: We are getting stronger
E147.description: After defeating Aragon we have become stronger and now we will begin to put pressure on Portugal in order to unite all of IBERIA.

E179.title: United Galicia
E179.description: We are now a united Galicia

E314.title: To Amsterdam
E314.description: It's time for us to finish off Holland. Destroying Holland will give the Germans an opportunity to spread even further. We must attack them within three months!

E306.title: Paktik
E306.description: The peace we need will be here and now.

E292.title: There are fewer and fewer of them
E292.description: We're destroying their bases, their numbers are dwindling, and that means communism is winning again. This is a great victory within Germany. But for them to fall, Wilhelm must be killed!

E275.title: Preparing the East
E275.description: After preparing the West, we need to prepare the East so that we can break through and not get stuck in the snows of Russia.

E175.answer1: This is the end of the road for radicals.
E175.title: Our Rome
E175.description: We were able to withstand all enemy attacks. Now we are a strong power and ready to say, "We are the true Roman Empire." HOORAY!

E172.title: Economic reform
E172.description: Even though we're at war, we began reforming the economy even before the elections, and we just recently completed it. This will be very beneficial for us during the war.

E240.title: Tea party
E240.description: Kaiser and Otto sat at the table, discussing what Germany had become and what it was prepared for. Now the Kaiser's storyline has come to an end, and I hope you, the player, enjoyed it.
E240.description1: It's very good that you got here.

E268.title: Take the economy!
E268.description: We may be military, but what kind of country is it without an economy? So we'll need to reform the economy and prepare it for our plans.

E174.title: January Peace
E174.description: Rome has surrendered. They have agreed to peace on our borders. This is a victory for us and our people. Hurray!

E239.description3: Encircle Poland and then we will go to Kyiv, Minsk, Riga and Petrograd
E239.title: Army Training
E239.description: With Russia aggressively suppressing Polish students and France gaining ground, it's time for us to prepare for any war. Otto advised us...
E239.description1: We will have to use small but good "fists" to put pressure on Russia, and at the same time, over time, bring down France.
E239.description2: We will need to quickly break through to Paris and destroy France.

E238.title: The rise of the Berlin Stock Exchange.
E238.description: The Berlin Stock Exchange recently peaked, demonstrating that Romea is no longer so majestic. So, Northern Europe is as completely dependent on Germany as Southern Europe is on Romea.

E173.title: Colonization of Tunisia
E173.description: We need a colony so that we can continue the war and get even more economy.

E363.title: Summer offensive operation!
E363.description: And once again the weather has softened our lives and we can fully attack Russia!

E237.title: Otto's Trips
E237.description: Otto von Bismarck had recently been urging neighboring countries to negotiate. And he finally succeeded. Now he will go to...

E264.title: Alsace
E264.description: We've at least somewhat stabilized the situation. Now we need to show everyone that we're still a force to be reckoned with. So we'll attack Alsace in three months. The main thing will be to take their capital to demonstrate our might!

E236.title: Majestic Teachings
E236.description: Our Emperor has issued a decree according to which we will conduct summer exercises with the Romans on a large scale in the Rhine. This will improve our Army.

E333.title: Fomenting revolution
E333.description: It's time for us to continue expanding the revolution. We'll start with a revolution in Switzerland! We'll help the communists there!

E170.title: Let's go to Italy
E170.description: Italy looks too aggressive and dangerous. To stop it, we need to conquer it.

E270.title: Fair elections
E270.description: We are finally ready to hold real and fair elections. We will calm the people and give them freedom. And the winner will be...

E235.title: The Great Reform of the Army
E235.description: Even though we've reformed the army, we're already a huge country, and we need to reform it again. Ultimately, we should, no, MUST, become a great European military machine.

E233.title: Czech Republic
E233.description: Bohemia also did not become part of us, because of the large number of Slavs, we decided to give them autonomy.

E253.title: Economic reform
E253.description: After all his travels, Bismarck decided to address the economic issue. Now that we're a huge power, it's become more difficult to control the economy. We're reforming our economy, and according to our plan, we're almost on track to catch up with the Roman economy.

E232.title: "To Alsace!" -
E232.description: These are the words our Kaiser spoke after announcing his plan. According to it, we must exert strong pressure and then send an ultimatum. This step would mean the COMPLETE unification of Germany.

E303.title: Paktik
E303.description: The peace we need will be here and now.

E384.title: Division of the colonies
E384.description: After the Great War, the question of colonies arose. Rome and Germany will divide them up as needed.

E353.title: Peace Treaty in Vienna
E353.description: Austria has fallen, and now the victorious countries have begun to carve it up; as a result of this conference, the Austrian Empire no longer exists.

E223.title: Ultimatum to Alsace
E223.description: After a complete victory over Austria, we sent an ultimatum to Alsace asking it to join us. This is important for us to gain greater control over France.

E330.title: There are more and more of us!
E330.description: We were able to reach an agreement with yet another republic. Even though they are social democrats, they were ready to join us. Hooray!

E186.title: We need to go to Africa
E186.description: It's time for us to start colonizing Africa and profit from it.

E356.title: It's time to implement the plan
E356.description: WE WILL ATTACK RUSSIA, just as we wanted. Our best ally, Germany, will be with us!

E228.title: Kaiser's victory in the elections
E228.description: The Kaiser won the elections, and he immediately declared that we were now great and would soon destroy Austria, too. It was time for us to become a real Empire. Hooray!

E266.answer3: Let's come to an agreement with them
E266.answer1: One army wasn't enough for them to march
E266.title: Fire in Hamburg
E266.description: Today, news came from Hamburg. A huge arson attack was committed against our government. They are still rioting in Hamburg. What will we do?

E265.title: Suppression of the Czechs.
E265.description: Riots have broken out in Prague, and to stop all possible riots there, we must suppress them. Let's enter Prague with troops and destroy their separatism!

E217.title: Preparing for the 3rd BV.
E217.description: It's time for us to prepare for the final blow to the head of the snakeAustria. By destroying it, we will completely unite Germany and become the strongest state.

E299.title: The first stage of French integration
E299.description: We are ready to begin integration with France to become a great country that will conquer the whole world!

E344.title: The second stage
E344.description: We continue the integration of Switzerland!

E263.answer3: Let them get what they want.
E263.title: Uprising in Munich
E263.description: Today, many citizens in Munich came out to protest our policies. They demanded change and more rights for workers. What are we going to do about them?

E153.answer1: Now the north of Algeria is ours!
E153.title: Money

E040.title: Venice?
E040.description: At this opportune moment, when Austria is weak, we have the opportunity to quickly aid the rebels in Venice and bring them back to us. Austria will only be able to protest; it will be unable to do more. For a united Italy!

E262.answer1: We'll have to resolve the issue with them.
E262.title: Control in Austria.
E262.description: After the fall of Austria, we installed a puppet regime. Now we need to resolve the issue with them. But first, we need to figure out what we're going to do with them.

E131.answer1: It's time to negotiate with them.
E131.title: Campaign against China
E131.description: We really need ice-free ports on the Pacific coast and for this we need to come to an agreement with China.

E312.title: The Murder of Marx
E312.description: Our agents managed to find and kill Marx in Switzerland. Now our main enemy within has been destroyed. And we can finally begin to develop!

E274.title: Preparation
E274.description: It's time for us to accept the fact that there will be a war in Europe. We've already seen skirmishes in Warsaw. And, in principle, the entire world is ready for war. So why are we lagging behind? Let's start training the Western army.

E022.title: March on Belgrade
E022.description: After Bulgaria, the road to Belgrade is open to us. Serbia and Albania won't pose any problems. In this battle, we will once again test the readiness of our army.

E129.title: Let's help Austria
E129.description: Austria is in a war of annihilation and we should help them because they are our allies.

E146.title: Victory
E146.description: Aragon has surrendered, and that's a victory. Finally, we've been able to almost completely unite our peninsula under one flag. And once again, VICTORY.

E145.title: It's time
E145.description: It's time for us to attack Aragon and take him over if he's not even trying to be good.

E361.title: Great War!
E361.description: The greatest war in human history has begun, the war that will end all wars. Let the world know who wins!

E338.title: New member of the ECC!
E338.description: Now Switzerland is also a member of the EU, and we will integrate it. But now it's time for us to continue resolving the problems with Spain!

E038.answer1: Now we are even closer to unity.
E038.title: Treaty of Rome
E038.description: After lengthy discussions with the French government, we were able to agree on a change in the Pope's status. From now on, the Pope will no longer have any territory in his possession other than a small parcel of land within the Vatican. Furthermore, the Pope will remain the head of the Catholic Church.

E315.title: Czechs
E315.description: While the military ruled the country, they forgave the Czechs, but the Czechs are not Germans; they are Slavs. We must destroy them and give even more space to our people!

E258.title: Great Reform
E258.description: We are almost completely ready for war, but many reforms still need to be carried out. So Bismarck has come up with a plan according to which we will carry them out almost simultaneously. This will be good for us.

E251.title: To Constantinople?
E251.description: We have had friendly relations with Rome for a long time, but until now it was unofficial. Bismarck went to Constantinople with a new purpose. He was able to negotiate the signing and worldwide announcement of an alliance between our countries.

E322.title: New Army
E322.description: It's time for us to create a new army so that all our conquests are better. But as good as it sounds, it comes at a price!

E144.title: Aragon. .
E144.description: Things are bad with Aragon, it's time for us to get ready and attack him.

E140.title: Granada?
E140.description: We have a particularly warm relationship with Granada. We liberated them and helped them. Now we are discussing our unification.

E143.title: Disagreements with Aragon
E143.description: Because of the recent problem we had in the alliance, people started to think that Aragon did it and now we have a tense relationship with him because of it.

E379.title: Let's end the puppetry in Poland!
E379.description: It's time for us to destroy her!

E318.title: They are with us!
E318.description: We've taken Amsterdam, and now Holland is surrendering. This is our first victory under Satan's leadership. It's a small but important victory. Hurray!

E347.title: The third stage
E347.description: We have completed the integration of Switzerland and now they are completely ready to join us!

E142.title: Portugal is leaving us
E142.description: Due to the interventions of Aragon and his party, Portugal decided to leave the alliance.

E036.title: Second meeting in the S-I alliance
E036.description: This time, we've begun to discuss unification in greater depth, and Palermo has already decided to embrace our unity. Italy will finally reclaim its place in history, but we are not yet fully one people. We will do everything we can at our final meeting.

E254.title: Studying in Bavaria
E254.description: Bismarck said: "We will reform the army and immediately demonstrate this reform to the world in exercises together with Rome. These exercises will be the largest of all!" Having finished something, Bismarck shouted - "BEGIN!"

E078.title: Albania for Peace
E078.description: Albania has peacefully agreed to join us!

E255.title: Preparation
E255.description: It's time for us to accept the fact that there will be a war in Europe. We've already seen skirmishes in Warsaw. And, in principle, the entire world is ready for war. So why are we lagging behind? Let's start training the Western army.

E310.title: Opponents
E310.description: We're already in power, but we still have opponents. It's time to put an end to themthe communists! We'll destroy them. In honor of the great Satan!

E139.title: Our Union
E139.description: Given the strengthening of both Rome and Prussia, despite our differences, we must at least form an alliance so that no one invades us or tries to capture us.

E374.title: Landing in the Baltics!
E374.description: Let's take Riga from the sea!

E138.title: Our history
E138.description: Our country, along with others on the Iberian Peninsula, fought against the Muslims, but we were never able to unite even after victory. Our goal is to unite Iberia and become a strong country.

E137.title: Winter
E137.description: Even though the enemy is advancing, our winter will not allow anyone to rest, but it will give us the opportunity to defend ourselves.

E289.title: Creation of the ESS
E289.description: We have formally agreed with the allied countries and now we have created the EU  the Common European Union. This will be beneficial for us all. And our economies will grow!

E297.title: Full integration of Hungary
E297.description: We have finally integrated the first member of our union. Now we are even closer to a unified state!

E136.title: The Great War
E136.description: We have been attacked. And now it is escalating into a Great War.

E291.title: Black Sun
E291.description: It's time for us to put an end to the Black Sun, the main enemy. We will fight them across the country, seeking out their strongholds and destroying them! Let communism be everywhere!

E135.title: Union of Poles
E135.description: We will finally unite all Poles into one state.

E119.title: Problems with Finland
E119.description: We were able to integrate them and now they will be part of our team!

E283.title: New connections
E283.description: Many countries have already begun to cut ties with us. But now we can contact other countries. Some countries are still communicating with us, too. For example, the Netherlands.

E134.title: We did it
E134.description: We won the uprising and now we are independent. Hooray!

E354.title: What will we attach from the puppet?
E354.description: Italy has become our puppet and now we can choose what to annex from it.

E293.title: The assassination of Wilhelm of Austria
E293.description: We recently tracked down and killed Wilhelm, the Black Sun's chief man. Now they are completely humiliated and destroyed, and we can finally attack Holland!

E124.title: The English?
E124.description: The Lord Protector of the KBO has come to us and proposed an alliance between our two countries. We've been friends with the British for a long time. After their arrival in Arkhangelsk, we began trading. So, your decision...

E133.title: Russia's order
E133.description: On orders from Petrograd, we will capture the insurgents in Warsaw and suppress them.

E368.title: Russia's defeat!
E368.description: After many long battles, Russia fell!

E132.title: Problems in Poland
E132.description: Hatred toward Russia is growing in Poland. We need to start doing something about it, otherwise it could lead to something else.

E030.answer1: Now all the problems are right in our hands.
E030.title: Question to I.P. Anatolia
E030.description: Anatolia is the most dangerous province; the Young Turks are itching to rebel. But we will carry out the Emperor's plan, adopted during the Council of Constantinople. Such a vast territory will initially weaken our economy...

E122.title: Campaign to Asia
E122.description: It's time for us to organize a campaign against Asia and capture Central Asia. After that, we'll look further east.

E284.title: The Austrian Question
E284.description: Austria is an autonomous region, and we need to integrate it into our great nation. And they're already rebelling really badly.

E121.title: The first army reform
E121.description: So, the reform Mikhail spoke of has begun. According to the plan, our army should be on par with Western European countries.

E116.title: Michael
E116.description: Mikhail Fedorovich won the election. He said he would improve the economy and wean Russia away from foreign dependence. He also plans to completely end the serf system.

E056.title: We rose up and WON
E056.description: Finally, the Red Revolution succeeded. HOORAY!

E365.title: Defeat of France!
E365.description: After many long battles, France finally surrendered!

E351.title: Integration of Poland
E351.description: Poland decided to join us. And why not? Now they're with us too!!

E309.title: Our exit
E309.description: It's time for us to emerge from the shadows and begin fulfilling our destiny. "We will do what we must, we will call upon Satan!" said Wilhelm of Austria. This will be a great era for us!

E118.title: Problems with Finland
E118.description: It's time for us to deal with the Finns, as they're the closest to our capital. This will also help us in the war with Scandinavia.

E054.title: Insurrection
E054.description: The peasants revolted again and even took Pest. This is very bad.

E052.title: Victory in our war
E052.description: We achieved the goals we wanted in the intervention in Austria.

E334.title: Diplomacy in Spain
E334.description: We used to have comrades in Spain, or more precisely in Aragon, but now they're gone. We need to start telling the whole world about this!

E021.title: Treaty of Burgas!
E021.description: Our diplomats managed to reclaim Dobruja. We didn't expect this region to slip away from our grasp, but Wallachia's fear made it relatively easy for us to gain these territories. They handed over Dobruja to us, and we gave them money and permission to use the ports.

E267.title: Take Alsace.
E267.description: It's time for us to attack Alsace as we planned. We must capture it quickly to intimidate the people and demonstrate our power to other countries!

E346.title: To Bucharest
E346.description: We'll get ready and attack Romania. They've been telling the world for a long time that we won't give up Transylvania. Even though there are Romanian people there. Maybe it would be better to unite them in our state!

E305.title: Paktik
E305.description: The peace we need will be here and now.

E123.title: The second army reform
E123.description: We continue to improve our army. With each new reform, we become even stronger. Hooray!

E117.title: Problems with Finland
E117.description: It's time for us to deal with the Finns, as they're the closest to our capital. This will also help us in the war with Scandinavia.

E282.title: New Year's speech
E282.description: Karl Marx began: "Happy New Year, comrades! Next year, much awaits us: new political connections, solving problems with Austria and becoming a great power. We will have to do all this!"

E308.title: Paktik
E308.description: The peace we need will be here and now.

E324.title: The end of the expanse
E324.description: Today we will end the unjust dispersal of Germans across different countries. We will take Bern and force Switzerland to surrender at any cost!

E125.title: Economic development
E125.description: While the army is important, what is a country without an economy? It's time for us to reform our economy and become almost completely independent from Europe.

E185.title: We need to go to Africa
E185.description: It's time for us to start colonizing Africa and profit from it.

E302.title: Defeat of Holland
E302.description: We recently took the capital of Holland, and now they're ready to capitulate. This is another victory for communism!

E019.title: Capitulation of Bulgaria
E019.description: The last of Bulgaria's forces were destroyed, and with them its very existence. Wallachia, as expected, managed to break away. Well, now we have only one grievance against them, but more on that later. We will fully integrate Bulgaria into the Empire. Well, congratulations on your first victory! (Prepare for war with Serbia and Albania.)

E348.answer1: At least someone is for peace!
E348.title: Romania's Ultimatum
E348.description: We sent an ultimatum to Romania, and they, realizing that they could not withstand our huge Red Army, surrendered to us.

E364.title: Defeat of France!
E364.description: After many long battles, France finally surrendered!

E120.title: Army
E120.description: As promised, our president began working on our military amid global tensions. Mikhail called it military reform.

E023.answer1: Even more lands for the Empire!
E023.title: Bosnia's Ultimatum
E023.description: Bosnia accepted our ultimatum to join us peacefully; it's the only option. Austria wouldn't be happy if we started a war on its doorstep. The main thing is that the Sarajevo government has realized its hopelessness. There's nothing left for us to do in the Balkans... except wait for Prussia.

E269.answer1: The third time will definitely be enough for them.
E269.title: Students in Frankfurt
E269.description: Today, students in Frankfurt took to the streets and demanded change. They are already destroying the city, and we need to stop them. What will we do?

E171.title: Romei's attack
E171.description: Recently, Romea attacked us under the pretext that we were too aggressive. This is a stupid reason for war. Our people will resist these invaders.

E018.title: "Let's end the threat!"
E018.description: All the troops are ready, right? Now it's time for us to break through. Our plan is simple: take their capital and the outskirts of their second most important city, Sofia. But we're not sure we'll get all of Bulgaria; the Wallachians in the north will probably want to secede. If that happens, we'll have no choice but to watch.
E018.description1: Let this be a small and victorious war!

E336.title: Revolution in Switzerland
E336.description: In Geneva, Switzerland, people began to protest en masse and demand that the government surrender to the communists!

E281.title: Integration of regions
E281.description: Even though we're bringing revolution to everyone, many still don't like it. So we need to bring revolution to everyone and destroy the opposition! And the most important challenge is the black sun!

E321.title: Switzerland
E321.description: Switzerland is also Germany in some ways, but they won't want to join us peacefully, so we'll have to prepare and attack them!

E020.description3: The army will be reformed with the help of Prussia; they are already strong "warriors." And the Young Turks must be stopped and not further fuel the conflict.
E020.title: Annual Congress of the Council of Constantinople
E020.description: Although we are the world's strongest economy, we also have problems in other areas. During the battle with Napoleon in Egypt, we discovered that our army was significantly weaker than other European powers. Furthermore, numerous attempts by the Young Turks to stir up rebellion became evident. We must either solve all these problems or try to mitigate them. Three levels of the council have put forward several options for us.
E020.description1: According to his plans, the army would be reformed largely during the war. Regarding the Young Turks, he said he would integrate them, like other peoples.
E020.description2: They plan to completely reform the army only after the military campaigns, and to accept the Young Turks into society.

E337.title: Victory of the Revolution!
E337.description: We won the revolution and now we will make Switzerland powerful!

E163.title: Elections in 1855
E163.description: Something strange happened in these elections. The Romans won with 96.7%.

E017.title: Bulgarian Kingdom
E017.description: The Bulgarian Kingdom will be our first target. Our treaty with Russia regarding the "independent" Balkans expired only recently. Neither they nor we fought or attempted to establish a sphere of influence in the Balkans. But it's gone, which means we can begin to act. Bulgaria has long been our enemy, and it's time to finally put an end to it. Prepare yourself, our Emperor!
E017.description1: We will call up the first infantrymen in Constantinople, the rest is up to you!

E016.answer1: This is where our great story begins!
E016.title: History of Rome (A small part)
E016.description: Romea, or the Roman Empire, is the successor to the legendary Roman Empire. In 1453, our country was on the brink of destruction, but Zacharias the Great, our savior, managed to repel the Turkish attack. He then managed to recapture part of our lands, ushering in our new dawn! Centuries later, we firmly established ourselves as the world's most powerful economy, and Constantinople became the world capital of trade. And now you're here; history depends only on you!

E257.title: The Central Bank of Berlin
E257.description: Recently, as our empire's economy expanded, a central bank was built in Berlin in this honor. Now we are truly on par with Rome.

E045.title: Victory in the Balkans
E045.description: We won the Balkans. Now almost all the Balkan countries are ours. We are ready for anything!

E130.title: Insurgents in Poland
E130.description: Today, a group of rebels took to the streets of Warsaw. We need to solve this long-standing problem.

E158.title: Our path
E158.description: We are united and now we need to choose a path through which we will continue to develop.

E278.title: The last phrase
E278.description: "We are a real Empire, and they are just liars. We will prove our strength, we will declare war on them, for the Motherland!" Bismarck shouted. And thank you for playing Otto. Well, good luck with the victory.

E187.title: We need to go to Africa
E187.description: It's time for us to start colonizing Africa and profit from it.

E081.title: Our Persia
E081.description: Our people have rebelled in Persia. Even though there are many sides to the conflict there, we must help our people.

E230.answer1: This is not the end, is it?
E230.title: Capture by the military
E230.description: Due to the election confusion, the military has decided to take power and will decide who will govern the country, but before that, they plan to do several things.

E044.title: It's time for us to unite under one

E063.title: Congress in Petrograd
E063.description: A conference begins in Petrograd today. Participants will discuss the fate of the world.

E234.title: The Central Bank of Berlin
E234.description: After the unification of Germany, we can consider our economy to be on par with Rome. To demonstrate our economic strength, we built the Central Bank in Berlin. We are now the second-largest economy in the world.

E157.title: Complete Capture of Algeria
E157.description: Now we have the deserts and resources we need!

E156.title: Army Reform
E156.description: We may have lost, but we are not broken. It's time for us to rebuild the army. Victory for the French army.

E043.title: It's time for Wallachia to unite.
E043.description: It's time for us to unite

E316.title: March Speech
E316.description: Wilhelm began: "We are already achieving success, our people are only becoming freer. We, Germans, will become a great nation, we will conquer everyone. The people and the state!"

E079.title: Serbia for Peace
E079.description: The Serbs peacefully agreed to stop this war.

E141.title: Trade between the alliance
E141.description: We are improving trade between members of our union and improving our economy.

E326.answer1: And we will attack our enemies
E326.title: Plan "Satan"
E326.description: We've almost completely united all the Germans, but we're still surrounded by enemies. So we'll have to DESTROY them all. Player, you've probably already researched the nuke. We need to create 500 nuke.

E345.title: The defeat of Spain
E345.description: We've taken Madrid, and now Spain is ready to meet all our demands. Hurray! Another victory for communism!

E300.title: Integration of France
E300.description: We will finally integrate the last country into our alliance. Now we are a united and great power. This is a great victory. HURRAY! HURRAY! HURRAY!

E111.title: Pushchin I. I.
E111.description: Ivan Ivanovich Pushchin is our current president. He's been in power for a long time, and there's been no improvement in his tenure. It's sad.

E216.title: Baten for peace
E216.description: Baten agreed to peacefully join and be part of our team. Hooray!

E290.answer1: Let's attack on New Year's Eve!
E290.title: Preparing a new plan
E290.description: It's time for us to take full control of Benelux. Holland will DEFINITELY not join us peacefully. So we need to prepare and attack them!

E261.answer1: They will be in our hands!
E261.title: Take power into your own hands.
E261.description: Even though power is already under our control, many things in politics exist independently; we will need to take control of them in order to implement reforms. After that, we will hold another election!

E095.title: Our ruler's travels
E095.description: Our ruler needs to travel to one of the countries in order to contact them and establish friendly relations.

E256.title: Preparing the East
E256.description: After preparing the West, we need to prepare the East so that we can break through and not get stuck in the snows of Russia.

E327.title: Development of the "Satan" plan
E327.description: We continue to develop our plan!

E287.title: Integration of Belgium?
E287.description: After Austria's integration, it's time for us to finally put an end to autonomous regions, so our Belgium also falls under this category. After its integration, we will continue to improve global connections!

E340.title: Plan "Geneva"
E340.description: Comrades, we have a new plan for integrating Switzerland into the N7. The entire plan will be carried out in three stages. After which, we will have to integrate Switzerland!

E319.title: The Fall of Alsace
E319.description: We have taken the capital of Alsace and now it surrenders. This is a victory for our army. Hurray!

E099.title: We continue the integration
E099.description: We continue integration and almost half of the people have already accepted our demands.

E202.title: Victory in the Fratricidal War
E202.description: We won this skirmish (perhaps not the only one). Now we are making our claims on Germany, which Austria MUST accept. Hurray!

E325.title: The Fall of Bern
E325.description: We took Bern, and now Switzerland has agreed to join us. This is a great victory. After all, now all Germans are finally united!

E183.title: Tripolitania
E183.description: It's time for us to start colonizing Africa. As a result of co-optation, we will have plenty of resources.

E383.title: Division of the colonies
E383.description: After the Great War, the question of colonies arose. Rome and Germany will divide them up as needed.

E091.title: Beginning of integration
E091.description: It's time for us to start integrating Wales. It will take two months at most, because they are very similar to us  the English.

E181.title: Egypt
E181.description: It's time for us to start colonizing Africa. As a result of co-optation, we will have plenty of resources.

E035.title: Congress of the Northern Italian Alliance
E035.description: After the Napoleonic Wars, the S-I Alliance was created on our initiative. Its goal was to defend our countries and unite our economies. But given the changing world, it's time for us to begin uniting, and we began discussing this at our recent congress.

E285.title: Army reorganization
E285.description: We need to reform the army to fit the communist model. We'll also need to change the officers' lounge and repress "unnecessary" people.

E169.title: The End of the Army's Reformation
E169.description: We've finally reformed the army. Now we need to prepare the economy. Romea looks very badly on us.

E323.title: Bloody Day
E323.description: This afternoon, our new group held a huge march against all non-Germans. Now there's a lot of blood on the streets, and even more room for our ranks! HURRAY!

E320.title: Suppression of Austria
E320.description: It's time for us to destroy this pathetic autonomy, and then we'll become even stronger. And we'll finally be able to influence Switzerland.

E317.answer1: Let's attack as quickly as possible
E317.title: To Holland!
E317.description: We will begin. Together, we will begin to expand our land. We are soldiers of a great country. Together and forever. For Wilhelm, for us, HURRAH!

E115.title: Elections
E115.description: Today, elections began, where the people must choose their leader. And they will be...

E127.title: Ship reform
E127.description: Our already aging fleets in the Baltic and Black Seas are in need of reform. We will replace them with more modern ones, and this is more than just talk.

E128.title: Growing independence
E128.description: We've finally become less dependent on Europe. Our economy is getting back on its feet, and we're ready for so much more!

E362.title: Tavrida operation!
E362.description: We will land in Crimea and on the Black Sea coast, this will be a good move for us!

E313.title: New plans
E313.description: Now it's time for us to think about foreign policy. We need to expand our reach so that the Germans have a place to settle. Everything for the people! And Satan...

E371.title: Scandinavian Intervention
E371.description: Against the backdrop of the Great War, Scandinavia decided to invade Russia and take Finland for itself!

E176.title: Rebels in Anatolia
E176.description: Our Emperor, there is enormous discontent in Anatolia and the Caucasus. We need to start doing something.

E114.title: The Death of Pushchin
E114.description: Today, I. I. Pushchin died. With his death, Russia will hold its second election in history. We hope the new leader will be better.

E042.title: Purchase of territory.
E042.description: The Kingdom of the Two Sicilies and the Kingdom of Granada are willing to sell us some of their territory for a hefty price. Will we take it? This could help us in the future.

E177.title: They rebelled
E177.description: Our Emperor, they have risen. We will have to suppress them to restore our dominance.

E360.title: We will help Russia!
E360.description: Russia was attacked by Rome and its ally Germany, we will not allow these two giants to expand even further!

E039.answer1: Now Italy will be united and GREAT!
E039.title: Treaty with Naples.
E039.description: The King of Naples also decided to join us peacefully. He realized that war would be pointless. But he refused full integration. After lengthy discussions, we were able to agree on their full political integration and partial economic independence.

E249.title: Full control
E249.description: We took the capital of Halsas, now they're surrendering, which means we've created that very GERMANY, the one they wanted and which we will preserve and make even better. For the motherland, for Bismarck, for the fatherland. And forward to COMPLETE victory!

E277.title: Great Reform
E277.description: We are almost completely ready for war, but many reforms still need to be carried out. So Bismarck has come up with a plan according to which we will carry them out almost simultaneously. This will be good for us.

E280.title: Planned economy
E280.description: After the revolution, it's time for us to destroy the old democracy. The first thing we'll do is build a new economyplanned! After that, we'll have to sort out our connections!

E113.title: Land reform
E113.description: It's time for us to implement land reform. It will help our economy, and our farmers will be able to breathe a sigh of relief.

E197.title: Our Alliance
E197.description: We have an alliance that we established over northern Germany after Napoleon. But the alliance is not a single state. So we will try to integrate them.

E055.title: Uprising in Lviv
E055.description: The peasants revolted again and now they've taken Lvov. But we were able to reach an agreement with them.

E273.title: Peace treaty
E273.description: We took Prague and Nuremberg (Bavaria). After that, Austria began to fall apart and simply couldn't resist, so this is the final victory over Austria and the UNIFICATION OF ALL OF GERMANY.

E112.title: Canvas of Cultures
E112.description: Our country is like a vast canvasa canvas of cultures. We are home to Poles, Ukrainians, and so on. But this also has many downsides.

E195.title: Our Story #1
E195.description: Our history is vast, and we've been trying to unite Germany for a long time. But something always goes wrong. This time, we can definitely do it.

E295.title: The first stage of integration of the ECC
E295.description: Although we have an alliance between our socialist states, this is not one single state, so we will unite and become a great country together!

E203.title: Second integration
E203.description: After the victory over Austria, we can once again try to integrate our countries and increase our influence.

E037.title: Unification of the North
E037.description: The third and final congress of the S-I alliance has finally taken place. We have fully agreed on unification. Now Italy will be written into history. Our future plans are to completely seize the Italian boot.

E298.title: The second stage of integration of the ECC
E298.description: Although we have an alliance between our socialist states, this is not one single state, so we will unite and become a great country together!

E294.title: War in Holland
E294.description: It's time for us to declare war on them, since they refuse to peacefully become part of the Great Suzerainty. They wanted it themselves, and we simply wanted a global revolution.

E357.title: We will help Romei!
E357.description: Romea started a war with Russia, we as allies will help her!

E259.title: The last phrase
E259.description: "We are a real Empire, and they are just liars. We will prove our strength, we will declare war on them, for the Motherland!" Bismarck shouted. And thank you for playing Otto. Well, good luck with the victory.

E098.title: Beginning of integration
E098.description: Let's begin with the most difficult integration for us, namely Ireland. The Irish are very reluctant to be part of us, so we'll have to spend more time on them.

E211.title: Plan "South"
E211.description: We have defeated Austria, and now we can implement another plan. According to it, we will send an ultimatum to almost all the German kingdoms in the south asking for their annexation. We will implement this plan in March 1853.

E110.title: Serfdom
E110.description: Although the Decobrites immediately abolished serfdom upon their arrival, its echoes still have a very strong influence on Russia.

E382.title: Division of the colonies
E382.description: After the Great War, the question of colonies arose. Rome and Germany will divide them up as needed.

E260.title: Peace treaty
E260.description: We took Prague and Nuremberg (Bavaria). After that, Austria began to fall apart and simply couldn't resist, so this is the final victory over Austria and the UNIFICATION OF ALL OF GERMANY.

eeditor.description:
Age of the Steam Machines

A map of Europe in 1851, telling the story of this world. While it doesn't have many interesting countries, it's ideal for a good game and immersive story.

The approximate content spans from 1851 to 1857 (59).

Brief Lore:

One crucial event occurred in this world: Byzantium survived. Zacharias I managed to repel the Turkish invasion and even recaptured some of its lost lands. After his victory, Byzantium began to return to the world stage. But to avoid confusion, Byzantium is the Roman Empire (derived from Rome).

 This event resulted in Europeans virtually not colonizing new territories (due to the preservation of the Silk Road), Prussia becoming closer to Rome, the schism of Orthodoxy, the victory of the Decembrists in Russia, and so on. Furthermore, Prussia synthesized the Leipoldite Crystal, which accelerated technological progress across the globe in all areas.

Recommended countries for the game:

1) Kingdom of Prussia - There's a good path to unifying Germany with wars against Austria. After its fall, there will be elections where you can bring in the Kaiser (the Main Path, which will be the largest in the future), Bismarck (the Small Path), the Communists (the Longest Path), or the Black Sun (the Slightly Crazy Path).

2) Roman Empire - A couple of elections and dominance at the actual start of the game. After some changes with Austria, there will be stagnation, but by 1857, things will get interesting.

 3) Russian State - A peaceful path of development and economic improvement. Integrating constituent entities and participating in a single BIG war.

4) Confederation of the British Isles - A path to national unification and the development of diplomacy to counter Prussia and Rome.

5) Sardinia-Piedmont - Unification of the Northern Alliance, followed by a similarly peaceful path to complete unification (wars will be added in the future). Then there will be a choice between a peaceful fall to Rome or a more radical path.

6) Kingdom of Castile and Lyon - Its own problems in the Iberian Alliance, and a military campaign against the communists.

7) Socialist Republic of France - A couple of events (will be reworked).
